                        <objectDesc form="codex">
                            <supportDesc material="chart">
                         <support>Textblock of straight-grained, ivory-coloured <material>paper</material>, with minimal external sizing and lightly polished, possibly handmade in the <placeName cert="medium" ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7000208" key="place_7000208">Indian subcontinent</placeName> with ~9 laid lines per cm and no discernible chain lines.</support>
